{"id":231967097,"title":"#機師 加拿大機師飛時法規(702)","content":"最近實在是飛到快掛了，想上來分享一下加拿大落後到不行的法規。\n加拿大商用飛行有分702/703/704/705，我是在702 Aerial work的一間小公司上班。\n\n702法規是這麼寫的：\n-過去30天內休3天就合法\n-過去90天內休13天就合法\n一般商用飛行員過去30天最多可以飛120小時，我們公司跟民航局申請，變成150小時。\n這個season 連續上14天沒休息兩次，9/3之前我必須得放一天假，不然就沒有休到13天了。\n\n加拿大的商用飛行員可以玩到很多亞洲玩不到的東西，像是702包含了空拍，開飛機灑農藥，在產油的地方跟著油管飛看看有沒有哪裡漏了。\n\n操歸操但還說到底還是蠻好玩的，像我昨天才飛著小小的Cessna，在40度側風27節陣風36節的鬼風落地，在飛行學校當教官可能玩不太到這種\n好啦抱怨完了，明天繼續上工朝噴射機邁進吧！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/nCJWteF.jpg","excerpt":"最近實在是飛到快掛了，想上來分享一下加拿大落後到不行的法規。加拿大商用飛行有分702/703/704/705，我是在702 Aerial work的一間小公司上班。702法規是這麼寫的：-過去30天內","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"5e4df604-ce17-49d0-a7bf-621022e76fc0","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-30T04:29:48.830Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-31T14:40:32.171Z","commentCount":20,"likeCount":57,"tags":[],"topics":["機師","加拿大"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"航空","forumAlias":"aviation","school":"多倫多大學","department":"機械工程系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":56},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/nCJWteF.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"66af56ca-b16b-4ef5-bdb5-dfeb941b007e","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nCJWteFl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/nCJWteFl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nCJWteFl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-30T04:29:48.830Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-31T14:40:32.171Z"},{"id":"66af56ca-b16b-4ef5-bdb5-dfeb941b007e","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nCJWteF.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/nCJWteF","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nCJWteFl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-30